---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---
<section id="sobre_mi" class="py-28 container mx-auto px-6 max-w-7xl">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
            <span class="text-sky-400 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm">SOBRE MÍ</span>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight">Sobre Nil</h2>
            <div class="text-gray-300 text-lg md:text-2xl space-y-6 leading-relaxed font-light">
                <p>
                    Soy un desarrollador apasionado por la construcción de sistemas completos. Me formé en Desarrollo de Aplicaciones Multiplataforma (DAM) y actualmente me especializo en Big Data e Inteligencia Artificial.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Mi objetivo es claro: no solo crear software que funcione, sino dotarlo de inteligencia para resolver problemas reales.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 mt-2">
            <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">What I Bring to the Table</h3>
            
            <details class="group bg-[#161b22] border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer open:border-sky-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-sky-500/5">
                <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 font-semibold list-none hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition">
                    <span class="flex items-center gap-4 text-2xl">
                        <span class="p-2 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-xl text-purple-400"><Icon name="simple-icons:react" class="w-6 h-6" /></span>
                        Frontend
                    </span>
                    <span class="transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-180 text-gray-500"><Icon name="tabler:chevron-down" class="w-6 h-6" /></span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400 pl-20 text-lg">
                    <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc marker:text-purple-500">
                        <li>Astro, HTML, JavaScript</li>
                        <li>CSS, Tailwind</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </details>

            <details class="group bg-[#161b22] border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer open:border-sky-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-sky-500/5">
                <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 font-semibold list-none hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition">
                    <span class="flex items-center gap-4 text-2xl">
                        <span class="p-2 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-xl text-blue-400"><Icon name="simple-icons:docker" class="w-6 h-6" /></span>
                        Backend
                    </span>
                    <span class="transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-180 text-gray-500"><Icon name="tabler:chevron-down" class="w-6 h-6" /></span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400 pl-20 text-lg">
                    <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc marker:text-blue-500">
                        <li>java, python</li>
                        <li>Spring Boot, Hibernate</li>
                        <li>Docker</li>
                        <li>Django API Rest</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </details>

            <details class="group bg-[#161b22] border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer open:border-sky-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-sky-500/5">
                <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 font-semibold list-none hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition">
                    <span class="flex items-center gap-4 text-2xl">
                        <span class="p-2 bg-pink-500/10 rounded-xl text-pink-400"><Icon name="simple-icons:scikitlearn" class="w-6 h-6" /></span>
                        Data & AI
                    </span>
                    <span class="transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-180 text-gray-500"><Icon name="tabler:chevron-down" class="w-6 h-6" /></span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400 pl-20 text-lg">
                    <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc marker:text-blue-500">
                        <li>Machine Learning (Scikit-Learn), pandas, numpy</li>
                        <li>MySQL, PostgreSQL, MongoDB</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </details>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>